<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 03 05 00 08 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的天氣這麼好，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人真想<delay8 />大顯身手，<delay20 />
好好做一頓料理呢！
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你常會<delay8 />自己做料理嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="02 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我很擅長喔！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="03 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">還好啦</message>
	<message label="001_c" attrib="04 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我專門負責吃！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇啊，<delay8 />真厲害呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay8 />正在練習<delay20 />
製作<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果大家可以帶自己做的料理來，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />辦一場家庭派對什麼的，<delay20 />
一定會<delay8 />很好玩呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來是這樣啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay8 />正在練習<delay20 />
怎麼製作<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先照著食譜上的步驟來做，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等到熟練了之後，<delay8 />再依自己的喜好加入變化，<delay8 />
這樣真的很有趣呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來是這樣啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay8 />正在練習<delay20 />
製作<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />喔。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想聽聽看專家的意見，<delay20 />
等到我變得熟練之後，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你一定要幫我試吃喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 04 01 00 02 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像今天這樣的天氣，<delay20 />
我都會把家裡<delay8 />好好打掃一下，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_a" attrib="06 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">是這樣喔？</message>
	<message label="005_b" attrib="07 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">加油喔</message>
	<message label="005_c" attrib="08 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">喔～</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我打算擦地板，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還要清潔窗戶，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常感謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我打算要清理書本的灰塵，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再用吸塵器吸地板喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實呢，<delay8 />髒污可是會<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />堆積在看不見的角落喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以今天我要徹底清潔一下！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 07 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能配合當天的天氣<delay20 />
來思考服裝的搭配……<delay8 />
這樣真不錯呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣的人有一種時尚大師的感覺，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得好佩服喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 03 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天要不要<delay8 />來做一點<delay20 />
<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />呢<tag a="110" b="0" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都會<delay8 />依當天的天氣<delay8 />
來決定<delay20 />要做什麼樣的點心喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 05 00 0a 00 00">像今天這樣的天氣，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是最適合洗衣服了。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />我從早上到現在，<delay8 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
就已經讓洗衣機<delay8 />轉了五遍呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。
</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 07 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下雨時，<delay8 />溫度和濕度都會有所改變，<delay20 />
所以烤蛋糕的時間<delay8 />還有材料的用量，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都需要<delay8 />做些細微調整喔！
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說……<delay20 />雖然我講得好像很厲害，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但這種日子，<delay8 />只要做些像果凍那樣<delay20 />
不用烘烤的點心就好了嘛，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 09 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飄落到手掌上的雪<delay8 />
一點一點融化消失……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在非常虛幻呢。
光是看著那模樣，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的內心……<delay20 />就湧上一陣酸楚，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="14 00 00 01 00 09 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天這夜晚<delay8 />真是太美好了～</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="020_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我見到了<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />嘛，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
就算四周很昏暗，<delay8 />
我還是看得到你的臉喔！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為練書法時濺到衣服上的墨汁，<delay8 />
看起來就不會太顯眼了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="16 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有什麼感到煩惱的事情嗎？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我的煩惱呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="022_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是想讀的書太多了，<delay20 />
所以怎麼讀<delay8 />都讀不完呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就是我太喜歡練書法時的墨汁味道了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />常會一直磨墨，磨到墨條都快用完為止呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣太浪費了，得想辦法改掉才行<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就是只要我一邊聽<tag a="135" b="4" arg="0xcd00" />
一邊煮菜，<delay8 />就會不小心聽得太入神，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果<delay8 />把鍋子燒焦呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="18 00 00 05 00 09 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天夜晚的星星<delay8 />看起來好清楚喔。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="024_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我很喜歡<delay8 />觀測星空喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道今天能找到幾個星座呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">只要看著星空，<delay8 />
想到無邊無際的宇宙，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再小的煩惱都能忘得一乾二淨喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">聽說星星的光芒要到達我們居住的地方，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實際上<delay8 />要花好幾十年、<delay20 />好幾百年，<delay20 />
甚至好幾千年<delay8 />的時間呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到我們正看著這麼久遠以前的星光<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是不可思議呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我在睡前翻了一下星空的攝影集，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果突然好想看看真正的星星喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果今天的天氣<delay8 />沒有太大的變化，
感覺應該能看見漂亮的星空，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真希望夜晚趕快到來呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像今天這樣的天氣，<delay20 />
感覺好像很適合觀察星星呢！<10_4 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果還能順便看見流星，<delay8 />那就太棒了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xc9 0xca 0xcb" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
有彩虹出現囉！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雨後的彩虹……<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是讓人心情舒暢呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
看！是雙彩虹！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻，<delay20 />只是在地面看著，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就已經覺得很幸福了呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的空氣很清新，<delay20 />
晚上<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說不定
能夠看見極光喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />漂浮在夜空中的光之薄紗<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是能看見，那真是幸運呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />極光……<delay20 />真的很漂亮呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，能跟你一起欣賞極光，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得好開心喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天早上有霧呢！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你的臉一片模糊，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來好柔和喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚嗚<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
從剛才開始<delay8 />就一直在打雷對吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真的<delay8 />非常害怕打雷<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你剛剛有看見流星劃過嗎！？<delay8 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果一直盯著天空看，<delay8 />
是不是就能看見更多流星呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為今天的天氣很晴朗，<delay8 />
我就在想，星星應該會很漂亮吧。<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果沒想到還有流星，<delay8 />真幸運！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">說到流星，果然就會<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人想要許願呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要用<colour id="1" />操控搖桿<colour id="65535" />抬頭仰望天空，<delay20 />
然後在流星劃過的時候<delay8 />按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />許願，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />似乎就會有好事發生喔！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但如果手上有道具的話，<delay8 />
就沒有辦法許願了，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以記得要空出雙手喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>